text: Creigiau Cwm-Ceriw a Ffos-las (Morfa Bychan) is a Site of Special Scientific Interest in Ceredigion, west Wales. ==See also== *List of Sites of Special Scientific Interest in Ceredigion Category:Sites of Special Scientific Interest in Ceredigion
